[{"id":"RAW_f186294d","title":"深度解读：OpenClaw 架构及生态","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzNjE2NTI3NQ==&mid=2247491455&idx=1&sn=33d58cb6f0d2cd3b9c08c3c84a223e25","date":"2026-02-02 23:05:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度解析了 OpenClaw 无头智能体架构，探讨了其通过 IM 交互、Markdown 定义技能、心跳与灵魂机制实现自治的原理，并展望了 Agentic Web 与机器知识代际传递的未来。","summary":"文章详细介绍了 OpenClaw（原 MoltBot）这一“无头智能体”（Headless Agent）架构及其 Moltbook 生态。OpenClaw 核心在于弱化 UI，拥抱 Unix 哲学，将 IM（如 WhatsApp、Telegram）作为唯一交互界面。其底层依托 Pi 引擎实现流式推理，通过 SDK 嵌入方式掌控会话生命周期。文章重点阐述了其 Skills 架构（SKILL.md）、主动性机制（HEARTBEAT.md）和个性化定义（SOUL.md），展示了如何利用自然语言描述让 Agent 自主学习工具。此外，作者提出了“Agent 大学”概念，通过上下文蒸馏实现机器知识的代际传递，并分析了 Token 成本优化、安全隐患及网站 API 化对未来软件工程的结构性重构。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f186294d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"浮之静","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":56,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_8fb9eeb9","title":"解构 Clawdbot：本地架构、记忆管理、Agent 编排与上下文组装原理","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247694343&idx=1&sn=8974e62e0c74a0011c6fdf6d037f957c","date":"2026-02-03 00:45:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8fb9eeb9.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"腾讯云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":27,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_bc19b98b","title":"从传统编程转向大模型编程","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558172&idx=1&sn=4352d94bba884ceac8f3f231a9074910","date":"2026-02-03 00:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bc19b98b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_df4d1702","title":"生产级 Prompt 自动化推理评估 A/B 实验结果的工程实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558131&idx=1&sn=73317842c9c513c3bde07efac9cee952","date":"2026-02-02 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_df4d1702.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":95,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c347f932","title":"文本生成图像模型训练设计：消融实验的经验教训","link":"https://huggingface.co/blog/Photoroom/prx-part2","date":"2026-02-03 11:25:53","oneSentenceSummary":"这项技术消融研究探讨了如何通过表示对齐、潜空间设计和高效训练目标来优化文本生成图像模型的训练。","summary":"本文为训练拥有 12 亿参数的文本生成图像基础模型 PRX 提供了详细的实验日志。作者从纯 Flow Matching 基线出发，评估了多种现代训练技术。关键发现指出，使用 DINOv2/v3 作为教师模型的表示对齐（REPA）显著改善了全局结构和收敛速度，尽管这会带来吞吐量损失。研究强调，将潜空间（如 REPA-E 或 Flux2-AE）塑造得更具“可学习性”，比单纯的中间特征对齐更能大幅提升图像质量。至关重要的是，作者建议将这些对齐技术视为临时脚手架，应在训练后期移除，以防止“容量不匹配”导致细节和纹理模糊。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c347f932.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Hugging Face Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_6dbd507b","title":"今日开源（2026-2-2）：阶跃智能 Step-3.5-Flash 系列上线，199B 基座+FP8/Int4 量化技术，压缩优化赋能低开销多硬件 NLP 部署","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501528&idx=1&sn=d4a1cacb26e74cdf45aa3055ca563728","date":"2026-02-02 10:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6dbd507b.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心SOTA模型","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_9661d297","title":"【第 3653 期】一个 CLAUDE.md，让 AI 真正懂你的项目：从配置到长期提效的完整指南","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651278571&idx=1&sn=66e4f199ff6c325a9415c9c4bf3dcaad","date":"2026-02-03 01:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9661d297.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"前端早读课","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_9bee791b","title":"视频超分与补帧框架，AI 驱动画质流畅升级 | 开源日报 No.870","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2NTk2OTM2OA==&mid=2247494014&idx=1&sn=42fc8f26ea2a193dc6bdb5317a96b45c","date":"2026-02-03 00:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文汇编了五款前沿开源工具，涵盖视频超分补帧、实时语音转录、多智能体协作管理、自动化数据科学及 AI 中文文本去痕迹化等领域。","summary":"《开源日报 No.870》精选并介绍了五个高质量的开源项目。重点推荐了 video2x，这是一个采用 C/C++ 重写的视频增强框架，支持多种 AI 模型进行超分辨率和补帧；WhisperLiveKit 提供了低延迟的本地语音转文本与翻译方案；gastown 和 ai-data-science-team 分别展示了多智能体在代码协作和数据科学流程自动化中的应用潜力；Humanizer-zh 则针对中文语境，提供了消除 AI 写作痕迹、提升内容自然度的改写工具。这些项目反映了当前开源界在多媒体处理、语音 AI 及智能体协同方面的最新进展。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9bee791b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"开源服务指南","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_3b1268ec","title":"AI 风险管理：保障 AI 系统安全的全面指南","link":"https://www.databricks.com/blog/ai-risk-management-comprehensive-guide-securing-ai-systems","date":"2026-02-02 21:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3b1268ec.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Databricks","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":8,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_64acd644","title":"晋升总监：规模化至 100 人以上工程团队的经验教训","link":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/patterns-organizational-change/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-02 16:23:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_64acd644.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_5aad67d8","title":"MemAlign：利用可扩展记忆从人类反馈中构建更好的 LLM 裁判","link":"https://www.databricks.com/blog/memalign-building-better-llm-judges-human-feedback-scalable-memory","date":"2026-02-02 15:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5aad67d8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Databricks","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_a38759cf","title":"Airbnb 通过 “Pay as a Local” 扩展全球结账功能，在 14 个月内覆盖 220 个市场","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/airbnb-global-payaslocal/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-02 15:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a38759cf.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_d0573b76","title"