,{"id":"RAW_ea35dfb4","title":"退隐 3 年后回归，周末写的 AI 一夜刷屏、一周拿下 10 万 Star 增速超 Linux，Clawdbot 之父首次长谈：如今几乎不看自己发布的代码","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247827870&idx=1&sn=3a2d4e170c491fcc462373b82704b762","date":"2026-02-02 10:20:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ea35dfb4.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":99,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_ea7e7995","title":"淘天集团自营技术运营算法团队 4 年 2 次荣膺 INFORMS“杰出实践奖”决选荣誉：以策略正则化突破 DRL 在库存管理中的落地瓶颈","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&mid=2650542682&idx=1&sn=4a56846c13628675c01337e79b01d614","date":"2026-02-02 09:05:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ea7e7995.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"大淘宝技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_8fbe16d8","title":"多维创新打造强泛化智能体模型，LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601 技术报告发布","link":"https://tech.meituan.com/2026/02/02/longcat-flash-thinking-2601-techreport.html","date":"2026-02-02 00:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8fbe16d8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"美团技术团队","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_41fe0f75","title":"2026-02-03 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-03-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-03 08:52:14","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_41fe0f75.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":68,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_fc8fb3b8","title":"喝点 VC｜a16z 应用团队：在如今软件可被快速构建的时代，护城河的重要性反而比以往任何时候都更高","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247513862&idx=1&sn=9a61f2ba2b4fcae7fc16eeef7986a406","date":"2026-02-03 02:54:00","oneSentenceSummary":"a16z 合伙人深度解析 AI 应用投资逻辑，强调在软件构建门槛降低的时代，护城河、专有数据及“系统级记录”地位是企业长期生存的关键。","summary":"本文是 a16z AI 应用投资团队的深度访谈综述。文章指出，AI 浪潮并非孤立周期，而是 PC、互联网、云与移动技术的累积爆发。核心观点认为，随着 AI 降低了软件开发门槛（Vibe Coding），传统的软件功能已失去防御性。团队提出了三大投资方向：一是传统软件的 AI Native 化，重点关注新公司的“绿地机会”；二是软件对劳动力的替代与增强，切入规模远超软件市场的劳动力市场；三是构建基于专有数据的“围墙花园”，将分散的原始数据转化为高价值的“成品”交付。文章强调，真正的护城河来自于成为不可替代的“系统级记录系统（System of Record）”以及对非公开数据的持续复利掌控。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_fc8fb3b8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Z Potentials","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":118,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_a9b9791f","title":"AI 干掉 80% App 实录：他用 OpenClaw 40 分钟完成自动修 bug、控制智能家居、通宵监控陌生人","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247625162&idx=2&sn=7a5d0f2560b51b067a8c003eff544b49","date":"2026-02-03 02:18:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文通过 OpenClaw (Moltbot) 创始人的实测案例，展示了拥有全系统访问权限的 AI 代理如何通过自然语言交互替代 80% 的专用 App，实现从自动修 bug 到生活琐事的全方位自动化。","summary":"文章详细介绍了 AI 代理工具 OpenClaw（现更名为 Moltbot）的颠覆性能力。创始人 Peter Steinberger 演示了该代理如何仅凭一张推文截图便自动完成代码修复、提交及回复，并展示了其在控制智能家居、办理值机、全天候监控等场景下的实战表现。核心观点认为，当 AI 具备电脑完整访问权限并拥有可累积的“技能系统”后，它将成为统一的交互界面，使大多数功能单一的 App 变得多余。文章还探讨了“零计划模式”这一新型人机协作范式，以及在极大便利性背后的隐私与安全权衡。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a9b9791f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"硅星人Pro","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_2a5415de","title":"⚡ 揭秘 GitHub 的 AI 革命：Jared Palmer 揭晓 Agent HQ 与编程智能体的未来","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/inside-githubs-ai-revolution-jared","date":"2026-02-02 15:30:27","oneSentenceSummary":"GitHub 的 Jared Palmer 探讨了从 AI 自动补全到自主编程智能体的战略转型、V0 的成功，以及作为开发者与智能体协作中心的 Agent HQ 的发布。","summary":"本文总结了对 GitHub 和 Microsoft 核心领导者 Jared Palmer 的深度访谈，探讨了 AI 驱动软件开发的下一阶段。文章研究了从简单的代码补全（Copilot）到能够自主执行复杂任务的高级“编程智能体”的转变。Palmer 分享了 Vercel 旗下 V0 的起源故事，强调了专业化 AI 工具如何彻底改变前端开发。重点关注了 GitHub 全新的 Agent HQ，旨在标准化智能体与代码库及开发者之间的交互。讨论还涵盖了技术障碍，如通过 Dev Containers 进行环境设置、模型选择策略，以及备受期待的用于现代代码审查的 stacked diffs 功能。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2a5415de.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":2,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_c3f36434","title":"AI 社交元年：Moltbook 背后的机机交互革命与行业新机遇","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650677128&idx=2&sn=ee75de9c09136a0b6c9f0a708c289a5f","date":"2026-02-02 13:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c3f36434.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"白鲸出海","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":38,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_9ffd5d0f","title":"Clawdbot 如何搭建永久记忆管理系统：全靠 MD 文档","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247522529&idx=1&sn=e5759a7d342a09ed485487c503a9c364","date":"2026-02-02 11:56:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9ffd5d0f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Founder Park","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":32,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_931d8aee","title":"最懂 iPhone 相机的人，回到苹果了","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1653501?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-02 10:29:52","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_931d8aee.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":22,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_91107228","title":"2026-02-02 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-02-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-02 08:45:56","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_91107228.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":92,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_1ab141d","title":"Codex 应用介绍","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HFM3se4lNiw","date":"2026-02-02 22:16:58","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_1ab141d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"OpenAI","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":8,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_635ddf0","title":"63.与 Rokid 祝铭明的访谈：AI 眼镜、入口与巨头环伺的生态之战","link":"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/6980029db4be4c149b8a115f","date":"2026-02-02 16:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_635ddf0.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","